Average Revenue Per User
ARPU represents the average monthly service revenue earned from customers. We believe ARPU provides management, investors
and analysts with useful information to assess and evaluate our service revenue per customer and assist in forecasting our future
service revenues generated from our customer base. Postpaid phone ARPU excludes postpaid other customers and related revenues,
which include wearables, DIGITS and other connected devices such as tablets and SyncUp products.(1)
